    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VAPT A4 — Update Phase & Status\n\n**Trigger:** Sub-workflow dipanggil oleh Bot A Dispatcher (`/update_phase`)\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Fetch semua proyek dari Notion DB-1\n2. Tampilkan daftar proyek (inline keyboard)\n3. Pilih proyek → tampilkan 8 opsi fase\n4. Pilih fase → tampilkan 4 opsi **project_status**\n   (Not Started / On Progress / Blocking/Delay / Done/Finish)\n5. Pilih status → input catatan PM (opsional)\n6. Update `current_phase`, `project_status`, `pm_notes`, `last_updated` di Notion DB-1\n\n**Session steps:** select_phase → set_phase → waiting_status → set_status → waiting_notes → save_notes\n**Database:** Notion DB-1 (Project List)",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 490
      },
      "id": "g7000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000015",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
